    {
      "chinese": "5月起，黑翅螢悄悄登場，台灣長臂金龜與為數不少的蝴蝶也很有看頭。秋冬季節來臨時，賞楓步道上會有大片的原生楓香林、落羽松、青楓等。",
      "ab": "buṟating ṟamagal la ga, mama’ matata’ mulaka’ malahngan kora’ ka yungyung. tamul, ṟapiriy ramas caṟung taxan kora’. patehuk pakmuhla’iy lu muhla’iy, minaring matanah ka ra’ paki’ Alang sani la. masinpayux ka iro’ na abaw ra’ taxan.",
      "order": "3",
